setViewDistance 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set rendering distance, in metres. Default is 900m (in OFP) or 1,200m 
 (in ArmA), accepted range is 500m to 5,000m (in OFP) or 10,000m 
 (in ArmA).  
Syntax:  
 setViewDistance distance 
Parameters: 
distance: Number 
Return Value: 
 Nothing